metadata.name: Homecoming
metadata.description:
The photo was taken in the Ödemiş district of İzmir, Turkey. The family members who worked in the field all day returned home in the evening, creating a beautiful view with the sunset. Photographing this delightful image made me very happy.

Photographer: Ahmet Çağlar

Photo size : 4500x3000 px, 300 DPI Edition: 1/1
